---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Contact Us — CalcTax"
  description="Get in touch with the CalcTax team. Questions about our calculators, found an error, or partnership inquiries."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 prose">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>

    <p>
      We'd love to hear from you. Whether you've found an error in our
      calculations, have a question about Canadian taxes, or are interested
      in working together — reach out anytime.
    </p>

    <h2>Email</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@calctax.ca">hello@calctax.ca</a>
    </p>

    <h2>What to Contact Us About</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Calculator errors</strong> — If you think a calculation is wrong, let us know the inputs and expected result. We take accuracy seriously.</li>
      <li><strong>Tax questions</strong> — We're happy to point you in the right direction, though we can't provide personal tax advice.</li>
      <li><strong>Partnership inquiries</strong> — Interested in partnering with CalcTax? We're open to relevant collaborations.</li>
      <li><strong>Press &amp; media</strong> — Need tax data or commentary for a story? Get in touch.</li>
      <li><strong>Privacy requests</strong> — For privacy-related inquiries, see our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> or email <a href="mailto:privacy@calctax.ca">privacy@calctax.ca</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
      We typically respond within 1–2 business days.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
